This is the beginning of a Dogfight Remake from
http://dogfight.kuto.de

It is currently playable, but very basic.
Everything is WIP.

Current Features:

-Two Player Game
-Windowed Fullscreen
-Only one plane type
-Four different Weapons (gun & (homing)missiles & bombs)
-Blank World (basic background and ground)

NYI Features:

High Priority
  -Game menu
    -Refine menus(background images, options etc)
  -Sound
    -Get better sounds
  -Better movement
    -Gravity effects

Mid Priority
  -Code cleanup
  -Comment everything
  -Background aka Tile Based Levels

Low Priority
  -A.I.
  -Ground structures
  -Many different planes
  -Many different weapons, depending on plane
    -Bombs (no rotation currently)
    -GroundToAir missiles
    -AirToGround missiles
    -Different gun types
    
    
Currently using Slick (http://slick.cokeandcode.com/) and LWJGL (http://www.lwjgl.org/)